Intructions to start the server:
1) ./server.sh <port> <number_of_players>

The server will wait until number_of_players connect to start the game.
The server will exit when all of the players are disconnected.

Intructions to start client:
1) ./run.sh <hostname> <port>

Two clients can not have the same name, if a client enters a name that already exists,
he/she will be prompted to enter another name.
